description:
The District of Saanich has published these datasets as part of its Open Data initiative. Saanich also provided the initial sponsorship in partnership with the Municipalities of Nanaimo and North Cowichan to create an Open Data Catalog for all Vancouver Island municipalities.

Initially formed under the Vancouver Island IT (VIIT) banner and now in partnership with CivicInfo BC, this catalog will ultimately become available to all municipalities in the province of BC with Saanich, Nanaimo and North Cowichan as the first government participants.
